{"type": "article", "id": 2989, "title": "Eley Kishimoto 衬衫系列", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-22T07:51:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232908yiSIsTFjA1XhKrRZ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t英国设计公司 Eley Kishimoto 日前联手来自 Shoreditch 的裁缝 Timothy Everest 与平面设计公司 New Future Graphic 推出了一系列手工丝网印制的几何图形花纹衬衫。Eley Kishimoto 赋予了每一款衬衫一个独特的模式，提供 6 款不同的几何图形花纹,将分为 Bold 与 Humble 两种款式，共 12 种选择，其中既有蓝粉相交的小格子图案、白色绿色相交的三角形图案以及蓝灰色的梯形格局图案等，在衬衫的主体、肩部、口袋、袖口以及颈部内衬均作了细节的花纹处理。这一系列衬衫将于明年 2 月开始销售。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232904kT26PJGZKu8Woqv0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232905mxcF9yf5ik2De4SE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232905oBP0QdA3HsfyuiqJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232906IczjGURrfp95gMmn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232906oPTKNyzOjGYui9q4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232907myGPUOfLwnbXFqjp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}